# Output format

Return a JSON object matching this exact schema:

{
  "okr_id": "{{ okr.id }}",
  "risk_score": <0.0 to 1.0>,
  "velocity_assessment": "<ahead | on_pace | slowing | stalled>",
  "factors": [
    {
      "name": "<short name>",
      "severity": "<low | medium | high>",
      "explanation": "<one sentence>"
    }
  ],
  "recommended_interventions": ["<specific action>", ...],
  "requires_intervention": <true if risk_score > 0.5 OR velocity is 'stalled', else false>
}

Output ONLY the JSON object. No prose, no commentary, no markdown fences.
